  "comparisonMode": "captured-vs-proxy-request",
  "notes": "Strict parity for customerMerge transferring a non-empty source-owned draft order. The proxy earns the setup draft through public draftOrderCreate, records the exact draft-order customer hydrate cassette used by that setup request, then runs customerMerge and verifies downstream draftOrders/customer_id reads move the draft from the source customer to the resulting customer while preserving draft fields.",
  "comparison": {
